# Insides
call:  "Insides on 5"
badge: 4-ball offense
desc:  The two middle players pick one target — here the 5th from the left. Hits from the center are hard to read until the ball is already gone.

setup:
  us:   10  balls 1 5 6 10   // middle two throw, corners hold
  them: 10  balls 3 8        // they hold the other 2

> Set — corners fake  (0.8)
  us 1 10 fake

> Insides on 5  (1.1)
  us 5 throw them 5, curve -22
  us 6 throw them 5, curve -14
